# Project Showcase: Benny Stores Credit Management System (BSMS)

The **Benny Stores Credit Management System** is a professional-grade, locally-hosted web application designed to digitize and streamline credit tracking for small to medium-scale retail businesses. It replaces traditional paper ledgers with a robust, digital solution that ensures accuracy, accountability, and real-time financial visibility.

